---
import { log } from "astro/dist/core/logger/core";
import Section from "../components/Section.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const works = await Astro.glob("./works/*.{md,mdx}");
---

<Layout>
  <Section id="title">
    <h1>CREATOR <br />FOR US</h1>
    <p><b>Son Inho / 손인호 / CYAN4S</b></p>
    <p>Game Developer / Web Developer</p>
    <p><i>홈페이지가 아직 공사 중에 있습니다. 양해 부탁드립니다.</i></p>
  </Section>
  <Section id="rl">
    <h6>FEATURE 01</h6>
    <img src="/rl.png" alt="RHYACTION LIVE" width="400px" height="200px" />
    <h2>RHYACTION LIVE</h2>
    <p>오픈소스 Unity 리듬게임</p>
    <a class="hyper" href="https://github.com/CYAN4S/rhyaction-live">
      BROWSE SOURCE CODE
    </a>
  </Section>
  <Section id="br">
    <h6>FEATURE 02</h6>
    <img src="/br.png" alt="Bouncy Rumble" width="400px" height="200px" />
    <h2>BOUNCY RUMBLE</h2>
    <p>공에 바람을 넣어 던지는 TPS 게임</p>
    <a class="hyper" href="https://github.com/CYAN4S/bouncy-rumble/releases">
      PLAY PRE-RELEASE
    </a>
  </Section>
  <Section>
    <h2>ALL PROJECTS</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      {
        works.map((work) => (
          <a href={work.url}>
            <h4>{work.frontmatter.title}</h4>
            <p>{work.frontmatter.description}</p>
            <h6>PLATFORM</h6>
            <ul>
              {work.frontmatter.platform.map((stack: string) => (
                <li>{stack}</li>
              ))}
            </ul>
            <h6>STACK</h6>
            <ul>
              {work.frontmatter.stack.map((stack: string) => (
                <li>{stack}</li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </a>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </Section>
  <Section id="about">
    <div id="about-grid">
      <div>
        <h6>ABOUT</h6>
        <h2>
          우리 모두를 위한 게임 크리에이터,<br />
          <span style="color: #26bfb3">손인호</span>
          <svg
            style="
            fill: #26bfb3;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            vertical-align: -0.4rem;
          "
          >
            <use xlink:href="/icon.svg#cyan4s"></use>
          </svg>입니다.
        </h2>
        <p>
          Unity를 활용한 게임 개발이 주력이며, 풀스택 웹앱 개발 또한
          자신있습니다. 게임 개발에 필요한 각종 리소스를 직접 만들어 하나의
          게임이 이루어지도록 합치는 방법을 잘 알고 있습니다. 또한, 팀
          프로젝트에서 협업 방식을 정의하는 업무를 주로 맡아왔습니다.
        </p>
      </div>
      <img
        src="./cyan.svg"
        alt="Cyan, CYAN4S's persona OC"
        style="max-width: 400px"
      />
    </div>
  </Section>
  <Section id="others">
    <h6>OTHERS</h6>
    <h3>EDUCATION</h3>
    <h4>금오공과대학교 — 컴퓨터공학과 학사</h4>
    <p>2017.03 - 2023.02(졸업 예정)</p>
    <h4>속초고등학교 — 과학중점</h4>
    <p>2014.03 - 2017.02</p>
    <h3>AWARDS</h3>
    <h4>2022 경북 게임인 해커톤 — 최우수상</h4>
    <p>
      <a class="link" href="https://github.com/CYAN4S/bouncy-rumble"
        >Bouncy Rumble</a>
    </p>
    <h4>우수 논문상 — 동상</h4>
    <p>
      <a class="link" href="https://github.com/CYAN4S/book-community"
        >Bookstamp</a>
    </p>
    <p>
      <a
        class="link"
        href="https://www.dbpia.co.kr/journal/articleDetail?nodeId=NODE11082600"
        >관련 논문</a>
    </p>
    <h3>SKILLS</h3>
    <h4>프로그래밍 언어</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>주력 — <b>C#, JavaScript/TypeScript</b></li>
      <li>다룰 수 있음 — C, C++, Java, Kotlin, Python, SQL</li>
      <li>배우고 있음 — HLSL/ShaderLab</li>
    </ul>
    <h4>사용 도구</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>주력 — <b>Unity, .NET, React, Next.js, Firebase, Node.js</b></li>
      <li>
        다룰 수 있음 — Supabase, SolidJS, Jekyll, Express, Vite, Webpack,
        TensorFlow
      </li>
      <li>
        참고: 사용 개발 환경 — JetBrains Rider, Visual Studio Code, Visual
        Studio, JetBrains IntellJ IDEA, JetBrains PyCharm, Android Studio
      </li>
    </ul>
    <h4>예술 도구</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>
        UI/UX 및 2D 그래픽 —
        <b>CSS/SCSS, Affinity Designer, Figma, Krita, SVGator</b>
      </li>
      <li>3D 그래픽 — <b>Blender, VRoid Studio</b></li>
      <li>오디오 — <b>FL Studio</b></li>
    </ul>
    <h4>영어</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>TOEIC <b>795</b> — 2020.12.13</li>
      <li>대학교 모의 TOEIC <b>805</b> — 2022.05.12</li>
      <li>영어로 된 기술 문서를 무리없이 읽을 수 있음</li>
    </ul>
    <h3>EXTERNAL LINKS</h3>
    <div class="grid ex">
      <a href="https://blog.cyan4s.com/" style="background-color: #26bfb3">
        <svg style="fill: white; width: 48px; height: 48px">
          <use xlink:href="/icon.svg#cyan4s"></use>
        </svg>
        <span>CYAN4S BLOG</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://github.com/CYAN4S/" style="background-color: #231f20">
        <svg style="fill: white; width: 48px; height: 48px">
          <use xlink:href="/icon.svg#github"></use>
        </svg>
        <span>GitHub</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://twitter.com/cyan4s" style="background-color: #1d9bf0">
        <svg style="fill: white; width: 48px; height: 48px">
          <use xlink:href="/icon.svg#twitter"></use>
        </svg>
        <span>Twitter</span>
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://www.behance.net/CYAN4S"
        style="background-color: #0057ff"
      >
        <svg style="fill: white; width: 48px; height: 48px">
          <use xlink:href="/icon.svg#behance"></use>
        </svg>
        <span>Behance</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://soundcloud.com/cyan4s" style="background-color: #ff5500">
        <svg style="fill: white; width: 48px; height: 48px">
          <use xlink:href="/icon.svg#soundcloud"></use>
        </svg>
        <span>SoundCloud</span>
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://www.instagram.com/cyan4s"
        style="
            background: linear-gradient(
                45deg,
                #fdd915,
                #fac520 10%,
                #ef4623 40%,
                #eb2028 50%,
                #ac3889 90%,
                #a53b94
              )
              border-box;
          "
      >
        <svg style="fill: white; width: 48px; height: 48px">
          <use xlink:href="/icon.svg#instagram"></use>
        </svg>
        <span>Instagram</span>
      </a>
      <a href="mailto:me@cyan4s" style="background-color: #666666">
        <svg style="fill: white; width: 48px; height: 48px">
          <use xlink:href="/icon.svg#email"></use>
        </svg>
        <span>me@cyan4s.com</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </Section>
</Layout>
